Sign in to a shared phone (Hot Desking)
This Help article is for the Cisco Video Phone 8875 Series and Cisco IP Phone 8800 Series with Multiplatform Firmware that registers to Webex Calling as a shared device. Sign in and book a shared phone so that you can use your directory number on it for calls and joining your scheduled Webex meetings.
If youâ€™re working in a shared workspace that has a Cisco IP Phone 8800 Series with Multiplatform Firmware and Cisco Video Phone 8875 Series available, you can sign in and book the phone to use as your personal device. Once booked, the phone loads your contacts, Webex calendar, and call history, allowing you to easily access and manage your communications. This feature enables you to work more efficiently and effectively in a shared workspace environment.
